document_data.mainbody: '''Hasbeen Road''' was a street located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Hasbeen Road was located in southeast Zhentil Keep in the [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]]. The road branched south then west off of the midpoint of [[Moonsea Avenue]] and terminated several blocks later at the wall of the [[Zhentil Keep/Harbor District|Harbor District]]. Hasbeen Road connected with [[Alley Way]].
